dcterms:description: The Personalized Image Prompt (PIP) dataset is the first large-scale personalized generated image-text dataset. It includes 3115 users and 300,237 text-to-image histories generated by these users using Stable Diffusion v1-5 and an internal fine-tuned version of Stable Diffusion v1-5. Each user in PIP has created 18 or more images and provided at least 12 different prompts.
dcterms:title: Personalized Image Prompt (PIP) Dataset
